---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Expert Guru Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 via-white to-secondary/10 py-20">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Welcome to Expert Guru! Your privacy is important to us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          At Expert Guru, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website, services, and products.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, date of birth, etc.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Academic Information:</strong> School name, grade level, test scores, subject preferences</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Billing details and transaction history (processed securely via third-party payment gateways)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, clicks, and other analytics data</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Any messages, emails, or inquiries you send to us</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Your information helps us to:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Provide personalized academic support and tutoring services</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Send important updates, class schedules, and offers</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Improve our website, content, and services</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Respond to customer support inquiries</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Ensure a safe and secure platform for all users</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sharing of Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We do <strong>not sell</strong> your personal information. We may share your data with:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Trusted third-party service providers</strong> for payment processing, email communication, and analytics</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Legal authorities</strong> if required by law or to protect our legal rights</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Our website uses cookies to:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Enhance user experience</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Track site traffic and performance</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Remember user preferences</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">You can disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We implement strict security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our services are intended for students under parental or guardian supervision. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You may:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Ask us to correct or delete your data</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
              Please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@expertguru.net</a> for any such requests.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90 mb-4">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">Expert Guru</p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Email: <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="underline">info@expertguru.net</a></p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Website: <a href="https://www.expertguru.net" class="underline">www.expertguru.net</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
